<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7427841>
    dc:description "Fig.27. Species erroneously attributed to Juga H.Adams &A.Adams, 1854. A. Goniobasis columbiensis Whiteaves, 1905, syntype (CMML 2042), original figure (Whiteaves 1905: pl. 2 fig. 11). B. Goniobasis rubiginosa I. Lea, 1862, lectotype (Graf 2001: 91) (USNM 119297), original figure (Lea 1863a, 1863b: pl. 38 fig. 193). Scale bar = 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7427841/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

